name: LA MUERTE  -  1/4 MAJOR ARCANA
description:
XIII. LA MUERTE

We should not be afraid of death, but above all we should not be afraid of the opportunities of life that death brings us.
The 13th arcane, the death, the beginning of my HENesis.

 - In 2019 I created my first tarot deck: El Tarot de la Fuerza, this collection of MAJOR ARCANA is part of its second edition -
